Name: sid
Desc: Array of HK\_N\_REP\_DEF elements. The i-th element is the SID of the i-th Report Definition in the RDL

Name: period
Desc: Array of HK\_N\_REP\_DEF elements. The i-th element is the period of the i-th Report Definition in the RDL

Name: isEnabled
Desc: Array of HK\_N\_REP\_DEF elements. The i-th element is the enable status of the i-th Report Definition in the RDL

Name: dest
Desc: Array of HK\_N\_REP\_DEF elements. The i-th element is the destination of the i-th Report Definition in the RDL

Name: debugVarAddr
Desc: Array of HK\_N\_DEBUG\_VAR elements. The i-th element is the address of the i-th debug variable

Name: servUser
Desc: Identifier of the application acting as user of the on-board monitoring service

Name: ctlRepDelay
Desc: Maximum reporting delay for the Check Transition List expresssed in multiples of the monitoring period MON\_PER

Name: lptDest
Desc: Array of LPT\_N\_BUF elements. The i-th element is the destination for large packets originating from the i-th LPT Buffer

Name: partSize
Desc: Array of LPT\_N\_BUF elements. The i-th element is the part size for large packets originating from the i-th LPT Buffer

Name: lptTimeOut
Desc: Array of LPT\_N\_BUF elements. The i-th element is the time-out for the up-transfer to the i-th LPT Buffer

Name: areYouAliveTimeOut
Desc: Time-out for the Are-You-Alive Test initiated in response to an Is-Application-Process-Alive Test

Name: onBoardConnectDestLst
Desc: List of identifiers of target applications for an On-Board-Connection Test
